                    <h2 class="text-center">Professional Career
                        
                    </h2>
                    <p>Before graduating from Shippensburg University in 2009, I had lined up a position with InfoGenius, a small web development company located in Allentown.  I have worked for the company ever since, and have helped create software and web sites while maintaining the company's existing code as well.</p>
                    <p>Working in a small team dedicated to development, I have been the lead, and often the sole developer on many projects that are further detailed on the <%= link_to "projects page", projects_path(:anchor =>"AlertBot") %>.  I have greatly enjoyed my time with InfoGenius, and consider myself fortunate for landing the position straight out of college.  Our primary brand is AlertBot, which is designed to monitor clients' websites and servers, alerting them via email or text message when their site goes down or behaves unexpectedly.  In addition to this service, we also record and analyze response data so that we may report on any alarming trends developing on clients' sites.</p>
